        <script type="text/javascript">
            //TODO: Performance - wtf is this and why is it in the page?
            /* Script to adjust placement of filter arrow for long filter names */
            (function ($, window, undefined) {
                $(function () {
                    target_trigger = $("#" + "makeTrigger");
                    target_container = target_trigger.parent();

                    if (target_container.height() / parseInt(target_container.css("line-height")) >= 2) { // If multi-lined filter
                        target_trigger.addClass("flyout-trigger-tip-tall");
                    }
                });
            })(jQuery, window);
        </script>

            /* Script to adjust placement of filter arrow for long filter names */
            (function ($, window, undefined) {
                $(function () {
                    target_trigger = $("#" + "engineTrigger");
                    target_container = target_trigger.parent();

                    if (target_container.height() / parseInt(target_container.css("line-height")) >= 2) { // If multi-lined filter
                        target_trigger.addClass("flyout-trigger-tip-tall");
                    }
                });
            })(jQuery, window);

            /* Script to adjust placement of filter arrow for long filter names */
            (function ($, window, undefined) {
                $(function () {
                    target_trigger = $("#" + "sellerTypeTrigger");
                    target_container = target_trigger.parent();

                    if (target_container.height() / parseInt(target_container.css("line-height")) >= 2) { // If multi-lined filter
                        target_trigger.addClass("flyout-trigger-tip-tall");
                    }
                });
            })(jQuery, window);

        <script type="text/javascript">
            //TODO: Performance - wtf is this and why is it in the page?
            /* Script to adjust placement of filter arrow for long filter names */
            (function ($, window, undefined) {
                $(function () {
                    target_trigger = $("#" + "mpgTrigger");
                    target_container = target_trigger.parent();

                    if (target_container.height() / parseInt(target_container.css("line-height")) >= 2) { // If multi-lined filter
                        target_trigger.addClass("flyout-trigger-tip-tall");
                    }
                });
            })(jQuery, window);

            /* Script to adjust placement of filter arrow for long filter names */
            (function ($, window, undefined) {
                $(function () {
                    target_trigger = $("#" + "doorsTrigger");
                    target_container = target_trigger.parent();

                    if (target_container.height() / parseInt(target_container.css("line-height")) >= 2) { // If multi-lined filter
                        target_trigger.addClass("flyout-trigger-tip-tall");
                    }
                });
            })(jQuery, window);

        atc.subscribe('complete.atcui', function () {
            var component = atcui.components.get('myatcModal');
            if (atc.URI().query(true).openMyAtcModal) {
                var cleanUrl = atc.URI().removeQuery('openMyAtcModal').toString();
                $('#myATCHeaderLogoutLink').attr('data-prev-url', cleanUrl);
                history.replaceState({}, null, cleanUrl);
                // Component will not exist if user is already logged in.
                if (component) {
                    component.open();
                }
            }
        });
